```

**Quick reference - what makes particles look good:**

| Property | Bad | Good |
|----------|-----|------|
| Count | 10 | 50-100 |
| Size | Fixed | Varies + changes over time |
| Opacity | Fixed | Fades out |
| Color | Single | Gradient over lifetime |
| Speed | Fixed | Range (min/max) |
| Lifetime | Fixed | Range |
| Texture | Square | Soft circle/custom |
| Blend | Normal | Additive for glows |

**The flow of a good particle:**
```
[Spawn] ──→ [Fade in] ──→ [Full opacity] ──→ [Fade out] ──→ [Die]
   │           │              │                 │
 small      growing        at peak           shrinking
 transparent  visible       bright            fading
```

